# Tech Stack

- **Framework**: React with TypeScript.
- **Maps**: `deck.gl` and `Carto Module` (strictly for handling layers).
- **Data Source**: Layers come from tables stored in Google BigQuery (via CARTO).
- Deck.gl documentation to follow: https://deck.gl/docs/api-reference/carto/overview
- Carto Module documentation to follow: https://docs.carto.com/carto-for-developers/overview
- Carto Build a public application HOWTO: https://docs.carto.com/carto-for-developers/guides/build-a-public-application

# Styling Strategy

- **Approach**: STRICTLY CSS-in-JS.
- **Libraries**: Use MaterialUI (latest stable version) OR styled-components.
- **Constraint**: Do not use plain CSS or SCSS files unless absolutely necessary for global resets.